for SimCLR, it's our model architecture. there are two things we might have missed, i am still checking:

1. we need to drop the projection head when passing to the classifier. we still train supconmodel with the projection head, it is only when training the classifier, we want the hidden representations instead of the projection head output

2. we need to apply dropout two times for unsupervised SimCLR. I am still looking at the paper for details of implementation
